<h2>The Legacy of the Realm</h2>
<p>
    In the age of steel and magic, <%- fillTemplate('<span class="gold">{playerText}</span> {isSinglePlayer ? "has" : "have"} set foot upon these dangerous lands.', {
        playerText: pluralize('Brave Soul', 'Brave Souls', stats.total_players),
        isSinglePlayer: stats.total_players === 1
    }) %>
    Through hardship and triumph, they have collectively ascended <span class="gold"><%- pluralize('Level', 'Levels', stats.total_levels_gained) %></span> in their pursuit of power. 
    Yet, glory always exacts a price, because <%- fillTemplate('<span class="hp">{deathText}</span> {isSingleDeath ? "has" : "have"} fallen in battle... lost, but not forgotten.', {
        deathText: pluralize('Champion', 'Champions', stats.total_deaths),
        isSingleDeath: stats.total_deaths === 1
    }) %>
</p>
<p>
    A few, overwhelmed by the weight of their journey, chose the coward's end, with <%- fillTemplate('<span class="muted">{suicideText}</span> taking {isSingleSuicide ? "its own life" : "their own lives"},', {
        suicideText: pluralize('Weak Soul', 'Weak Souls', stats.total_players_suicided),
        isSingleSuicide: stats.total_players_suicided === 1
    }) %>
    while <%- fillTemplate('<span class="hp">{cheatText}</span> {isSingleCheat ? "was" : "were"} struck down by the gods for attempting to bypass the laws of the realm.', {
        cheatText: pluralize('Heretic', 'Heretics', stats.total_players_cheated),
        isSingleCheat: stats.total_players_cheated === 1
    }) %>
</p>

<h2>Echoes of the Battlefield</h2>
<p>
    The drums of war never truly fall silent because <%- fillTemplate('<span class="gold">{battleText}</span> {isSingleBattle ? "has" : "have"} been fought against the encroaching darkness,', {
        battleText: pluralize('Battle', 'Battles', stats.total_battles),
        isSingleBattle: stats.total_battles === 1
    }) %>
    resulting in the defeat of <span class="gold"><%- pluralize('Formidable Foe', 'Formidable Foes', stats.total_enemies_killed) %></span>. 
</p>
<p>
    From these conflicts, the survivors extracted vast wisdom, gaining a total of <span class="xp"><%= stats.total_xp_gained_formatted %> XP</span>. 
    <%- fillTemplate("But the wild is treacherous, as the hunters became the hunted and <span class=\"hp\">{ambushText}</span> {isSingleAmbush ? 'has' : 'have'} occurred, nearly claiming those who walked unprepared.", {
        ambushText: pluralize('Ambush', 'Ambushes', stats.total_ambushes),
        isSingleAmbush: stats.total_ambushes === 1
    }) %>
</p>

<h2>The Toll of Survival</h2>
<p>
    Hardship is measured in blood and resilience. Our champions have shed <span class="hp"><%= stats.total_hp_lost_formatted %> HP</span>, 
    flesh torn by tooth and claw. Yet, the craft of the blacksmith has proven its worth, as armor deflected <span class="muted"><%= stats.total_damage_blocked_formatted %> Damage</span>. 
</p>
<p>
    To mend their broken bodies, they have sought the warmth of the Inn and the delicious food inside, healing for a combined total of <span class="heal"><%= stats.total_hp_healed_formatted %> HP</span>.
</p>

<h2>The Flow of Fortune</h2>
<p>
    Wealth flows like a river through the pockets of the daring. A massive sum of <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena_generated_formatted %> Adena</span> has been pulled from the corpses of monsters and the hidden corners of the world. 
    Most of this fortune, however, returns to the realm's economy since <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena_spent_formatted %> Adena</span> has been spent on provisions and equipment. 
</p>
<p> 
    The shops have flourished, selling <span class="gold"><%- pluralize('Weapon', 'Weapons', stats.total_weapons_bought) %></span> and <span class="gold"><%- pluralize('Armor', 'Armors', stats.total_armors_bought) %></span> to those who would be king, 
    while the local Inn has served <span class="gold"><%- pluralize('Meal', 'Meals', stats.total_food_bought) %></span> to keep the fires of life burning. 
    <!-- Today, the total wealth held within the pouches of all active wanderers stands at <span class="gold">🪙 <%= stats.total_adena_formatted %> Adena</span>. -->
</p>

<p class="last">
    <a href="/">Go back to game start</a>
</p>
